{"tid":1529484,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"91香港人鄧寇克大行動","createTime":"2019-09-01T17:52:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T20:11:48.000Z","uid":309002,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"21c2d3dd542cb8bf86bff66c9b2247f9ae8687a7","tid":1529484,"uid":309002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:52:31.000Z","msg":"一路睇大家入機場接人就覺得同 鄧寇克大行動 呢套戲嘅情節好相似<br />\n大家由機場行去公路再到青馬大橋再上公路行<br />\n到有各位市民等住接載<br />\n同戲內英國船家平民全部出揸船去法國救士兵 <br />\n成班士兵坐市民嘅船翻到英國行路軌一樣咁深刻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hnKgWFn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhnKgWFn.jpg&h=15103659&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/frtYqyH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfrtYqyH.jpg&h=6045a2d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qGXY90o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqGXY90o.jpg&h=68b8657c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPoEUr3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPoEUr3.jpg&h=886f924c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DruTYTK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDruTYTK.jpg&h=bdc53efc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">辛苦晒各位義士 好好休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n記得戲入邊成班士兵落船係火車站行<br />\n有個伯伯派物資比士兵<br />\n個主角同伯伯講佢哋冇打贏到<br />\n個伯伯話：<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>翻到黎已經好好</strong></span><br />\n佢講得好有道理<br />\n我哋要同呢個政府鬥長命<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔可以再流血再被捕 <br />\n一個都不能少要記住犧牲左嘅義士手足<br />\n唔可以白費大家嘅付出<br />\n各位加油</strong></span><br />\n光復香港時代革命"},{"pid":"9ad2019951f7b01ed7763690d2ddf9588354db8e","tid":1529484,"uid":309002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:52:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bda7491e8ee9dabfe90c6f25f3db3935ceb776c9","tid":1529484,"uid":309002,"like":0,"